  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If you successfully grapple a creature, you can use your reaction to make a bite attack against that creature. A bite attack is an unarmed strike that deals 1d4 piercing damage. In addition, any creature struck must make a Constitution Saving throw (DC 10 + your proficiency bonus) or become poisoned for one minute.</p>",
